}
```

**Return type note:** The client types show `Ml_RegisterModelGroup_ResponseBody = Ml_Common.ModelGroupRegistration` which is `{ model_group_id: string; status: string; }`.

#### 3.3 `registerModel({ name, version, modelGroupId, modelFormat })`

```typescript
@LogExecution()
async registerModel({
  name,
  version,
  modelGroupId,
  modelFormat,
}: {
  name: string;
  version: string;
  modelGroupId: string;
  modelFormat: 'TORCH_SCRIPT' | 'ONNX';
}): Promise<{ taskId: string; status: string }> {
